Description: Curated GeoTIFF layers for teaching and experimentation with
    Zonation and ZonationR. Rasters use WGS84 (EPSG:4326). This is not a
    definitive research-grade dataset. Raw rasters live under 'inst/extdata/'
    as recommended for non-R data in R Packages (2e). See 'inst/extdata/metadata.md'
    for sources, layer layout, and attribution.
